Hispanic Sociolinguistics
======
This seminar is an introduction into the various methodologies and concepts of the field of sociolinguistics and explore topics related to the Spanish language. The seminar will cover both qualitative and quantitative sociolinguistic approaches to linguistic variation and change. 
